  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ParamsInitializer<ImageInitParams>, Provider<Mask>, ProviderAsStack

    public class InsideBoxOn
extends FromDimensionsBase
    Creates a binary img-channel where all pixels are 'on' within a certain x, y, z coordinate range

    This effectively creates a mask that is a box
